adornment_list.name: Terror Yaulp
adornment_list.description: A yaulp of terror emitted from the mace that increases your power, strength, and lowers your hate with the enemy.

effect_list.description: On any combat or spell hit this spell may cast Terror Yaulp on target of attack.  Lasts for 36.0 seconds.  Triggers about 1.8 times per minute.
Increases STR, AGI, INT and WIS of caster by 31.0
Increases Max Power of caster by 292.5
Cannot be modified except by direct means

adornment_list.name: Journeyman's Boots
adornment_list.description: Increases the run speed of the wearer. Does not stack with other run speed augmentations.

item.description: Quiver that can be placed in your ammo slot that holds arrows to be used while using a ranged weapon.  This is the only item that can be held in this container

adornment_list.name: Haste
adornment_list.description: The power of the Flowing Black Silk Sash allows you to attack far more quickly.

effect_list.description: Reduces cast time of all spells by 5 percent.
